    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >TRI-GER is a vector based top down shoot-em-up inspired by classic arcade games. With your ability to switch colors and upgrade your arsenal, your job is to fight endless waves of multi-color enemy insectoids and maximize your high score. Match the color of your blaster with the enemies you're shooting to increase your damage and rack up combos, but be careful! Color matching is a two way street, so enemies that share your color have the same advantages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697010/extras/261d498af2a85439854d6cd94fb3587b.poster.avif?t=1761862285\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697010/extras/261d498af2a85439854d6cd94fb3587b.webm?t=1761862285\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697010/extras/261d498af2a85439854d6cd94fb3587b.mp4?t=1761862285\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br>Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Switch between 3 colors to maximize damage dealt to enemy insectoids</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697010/extras/9c73e62e3296afd305c309b72e44066a.poster.avif?t=1761862285\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697010/extras/9c73e62e3296afd305c309b72e44066a.webm?t=1761862285\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697010/extras/9c73e62e3296afd305c309b72e44066a.mp4?t=1761862285\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrades for both you and the insectoids as the game progresses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697010/extras/305c392debe1a9b388186ec95a76de08.poster.avif?t=1761862285\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697010/extras/305c392debe1a9b388186ec95a76de08.webm?t=1761862285\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697010/extras/305c392debe1a9b388186ec95a76de08.mp4?t=1761862285\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boss battles at the end of every wave</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697010/extras/3bb44a2e254cab4de9746c6982820cc8.poster.avif?t=1761862285\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697010/extras/3bb44a2e254cab4de9746c6982820cc8.webm?t=1761862285\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697010/extras/3bb44a2e254cab4de9746c6982820cc8.mp4?t=1761862285\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A radiance meter to build up and activate a temporary invincible mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697010/extras/dab88db4ecb2b4c536d9dfe22e7bc9de.poster.avif?t=1761862285\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697010/extras/dab88db4ecb2b4c536d9dfe22e7bc9de.webm?t=1761862285\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697010/extras/dab88db4ecb2b4c536d9dfe22e7bc9de.mp4?t=1761862285\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Support for color blindness via dynamic desaturation of certain hues.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
